## ✅ 6. Inventory

| # | Action | Expected Result |
|---|--------|----------------|
| 6.1 | Navigate to `/inventory` | Shows Fruiting Batches section and Stored Items section |
| 6.2 | Click **Add Item** | Dialog opens with Name, Type, Quantity, Unit, Preserved checkbox |
| 6.3 | Add a Liquid-Culture item | Appears in Stored Items table |
| 6.4 | Add same item (same Name+Type+Preserved) again | Quantity stacks (merges into same row) |
| 6.5 | Edit item quantity | Quantity updates in table |
| 6.6 | Delete an item | Item removed from table |
| 6.7 | Check **Source** column for harvested items | Shows the culture source (e.g. "Master-LC-001") |
| 6.8 | Check **Date Added to Storage** column | Shows the `createdAt` date of the inventory record |
| 6.9 | Use the search box | Filters by item name in real-time |
| 6.10 | Convert a Fresh jar to Dried | Jar qty decreases by 1; a Dried row appears/increments |

