## ✅ 7. Settings

| # | Action | Expected Result |
|---|--------|----------------|
| 7.1 | Navigate to `/settings` | Room dimensions and shake times visible |
| 7.2 | Update room width/height | Values persist on reload |
| 7.3 | Update shake morning/evening time | Times persist; LC shake alerts use these thresholds |
| 7.4 | Trigger **Export DB** | Browser downloads a `.sqlite` file |
| 7.5 | Trigger **Import DB** | Loads a previously exported `.sqlite` and refreshes all data |
| 7.6 | Change app theme | Theme persists on reload (light/dark/nature/cordyceps/midnight) |

