## ⚠️ Known Behaviors (Not Bugs)

| Behavior | Explanation |
|----------|-------------|
| Harvesting same batch type twice merges inventory | [harvestBatchService](file:///d:/myworks/Mushroom_Operations/lib/services/production.ts#100-166) accumulates into an existing row by Name+Type |
| Past Location shows primary rack only for harvested batches | `batchLocations` are cleared on harvest; only the original rack/layer is shown |
| Discarded Date may show wrong date for old batches | `updatedAt` was not stamped before discarding — only new discards are accurate |
| Dashboard counts use the **Node.js [sqlite.db](file:///d:/myworks/Mushroom_Operations/sqlite.db)** if running scripts, but browser uses IndexedDB | These are separate databases; scripts are for testing service logic, browser is production |

---

## 🔁 Re-running Backend Tests

```bash
npx tsx scripts/run-all-tests.ts
```

All 38 tests should pass. Tests automatically seed and clean up their own data.
